### Cron Spider TypeScript API 示例
### 可以使用 VS Code 的 REST Client 扩展或其他 HTTP 客户端工具

### 1. 获取服务状态
GET http://localhost:3001/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. 获取健康检查
GET http://localhost:3001/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. 获取所有任务
GET http://localhost:3001/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. 创建价格监控任务
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "price-monitor-example",
  "schedule": "0 */5 * * * *",
  "url": "https://httpbin.org/json",
  "selector": "",
  "webhook": "",
  "startImmediately": false,
  "headers": {
    "User-Agent": "Cron Spider Bot"
  },
  "timeout": 10000,
  "maxRetries": 3
}

###

### 5. 创建并立即启动任务
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "news-scraper",
  "schedule": "0 0 */6 * * *",
  "url": "https://httpbin.org/html",
  "selector": "h1",
  "webhook": "https://webhook.site/your-unique-id",
  "startImmediately": true
}

###

### 6. 获取单个任务状态
GET http://localhost:3001/tasks/price-monitor-example
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. 启动任务
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks/price-monitor-example/start
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 8. 手动执行任务
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks/price-monitor-example/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://httpbin.org/json",
  "selector": "",
  "webhook": "https://webhook.site/test"
}

###

### 9. 停止任务
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks/price-monitor-example/stop
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 10. 重启任务
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks/price-monitor-example/restart
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 11. 删除任务
DELETE http://localhost:3001/tasks/price-monitor-example
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 12. 测试错误处理 - 创建重复任务名称
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "duplicate-task",
  "schedule": "0 * * * * *",
  "url": "https://httpbin.org/json"
}

###

### 13. 测试错误处理 - 无效的 cron 表达式
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "invalid-cron-task",
  "schedule": "invalid-cron-expression",
  "url": "https://httpbin.org/json"
}

###

### 14. 测试错误处理 - 无效的URL
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "invalid-url-task",
  "schedule": "0 * * * * *",
  "url": "not-a-valid-url"
}

###